'''Francis Borelli''' (8 April 1932 &ndash; 2 October 2007) was a [[France|French]] businessman. He was the chairman of the [[Association football|football]] club [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]] from 1978 to 1991.

